<p> </p>
<div style="border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top:solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left:none; border-right:none; padding:1.0pt 0in 1.0pt 0in">
<p style="border:none; padding:0in"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">Hospital Acquired Pneumonia (HAP) and Ventilator Associated Pneumonia (VAP)</span></span></b></span></span></span></p>
</div>
<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Background</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<ul>
<li style="list-style-type:none">
<ul>
<li style="list-style-type:none">
<ul>
<li style="list-style-type:none">
<ul>
<li style="list-style-type:none">
<ul>
<li style="list-style-type:none"> </li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background:white"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">HAP: Pneumonia that develops &gt;48 hours after admission</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background:white"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">VAP: Pneumonia that develops &gt;48 hours after endotracheal intubation </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left:25px; text-indent:-9.35pt"> </p>
<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Evaluation</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<ul>
<li style="list-style-type:none">
<ul>
<li style="list-style-type:none">
<ul>
<li style="list-style-type:none">
<ul>
<li style="list-style-type:none">
<ul>
<li style="list-style-type:none"> </li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background:white"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Cultures of blood, sputum, endotracheal aspirate and/or bronchoscopy specimen</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background:white"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Consider MRSA nares to help with de-escalation</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background:white"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">If there is concern for respiratory viruses, influenza, COVID send RVP </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left:25px"> </p>
<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Management</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<ul>
<li style="list-style-type:none">
<ul>
<li style="list-style-type:none">
<ul>
